Titolo: A Fairy Tale (video game)

Anno: 2009

Descrizione: A Fairy Tale is a game that was released by Reflexive Entertainment. A Fairy Tale was initially PC exclusive, however, it was later released on Nintendo DS. The game is a matching game that is similar to the popular match-3 video games, but is unique in its gameplay. The game follows the adventures of three young fairies journeying through the forest as they attempt to save their village from an evil menace. The game also features a running comedic story with tongue-in-cheek storyboards.